{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eafd5683f7fb29a640a0170e97ad6","seq":3,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T20:46:32","note":"open → in_progress. B5 LIVE SESSION 1 (2026-06-10, owner + agent): INDEX-SCENARIO CORE PROVEN — send (two-write submit) → real Claude Code answers → passive detection (settle_prompt, NBSP-aware ^❯\\s prompt regex, 'esc to interrupt' busy marker) → armed one-shot consumed exactly once → agent_relay.turn_completed emitted + accepted by Minerva ([MCP STDIO Async]). Human turns never armed (typed/drafted in same terminal throughout = non-interference exercised continuously). read_clean live (chrome+redaction). Final pass ran on SEED calibration (3c0d6e4) with zero runtime tuning. Five lessons shipped as fixes: paste-vs-Enter two-write send, literal-escape trim, broker envelope unwrap (+ tests now speak production envelope), wait-loop pacing, timeout-waits still run detection, NBSP calibration. REMAINING for done: read_turn row-window fix (019eb345d4d9) then live distill (model_spec) + delivery legs; PLUGIN_EVENT trigger → chat wake leg (A6 integration); codex/opencode profile calibration; formal byte-level non-interference proof. Plugins main @ 3c0d6e4 (5 fix commits this session, local)."}
