{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eb31f08697ecfa50c8c6f16ecc236","seq":5,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T22:30:49","note":"in_progress → done. Shipped plugins main 9e4da87 (same pass as relay_ask, which subsumes it for the ask case). HITL-PASSED live 2026-06-10: core terminal_write (never arms) submitted a human-style turn; wait_turn blocked and returned {cause:turn_completed, method:settle_prompt, timed_out:false} — pull-side visibility of unarmed turns without busy-polling watch_status. Wakes on ANY counted detection via the turn-cache detection_serial (gated phantoms never bump). Timeout path integration-tested (gated idle screen never counts)."}
