{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eb32faa4d7a2c8771543ab03798ec","seq":5,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T21:46:39","note":"in_progress → done. Shipped plugins main cd404f4 (with lifecycle item, one state file as planned). state.rs → <exe_dir>/agent_relay_state.json (codetools os.Executable precedent — host SubProcess can't chdir so cwd is Minerva's; exe dir IS the plugin data dir). Persists profile OVERRIDES only (entries differing from builtin seeds — untouched profiles keep tracking future shipped calibrations, avoiding the stale-seed shadow), filter rules, watch sessions. Saved on every mutation, loaded at startup. AGENT_RELAY_STATE_FILE env override (empty = disabled) keeps integration tests hermetic. File gitignored (side-load exe dir = dev source dir)."}
