{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eb345d4d972bf84c43a78cc8163f4","seq":5,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T21:38:05","note":"in_progress → done. Shipped plugins main a775751 + 23a5120. Three boundary bugs fixed: (1) snapshot moved BEFORE the writes — post-write snapshot raced the TUI busy block which occupies MORE rows than the final answer layout, answer rendered ABOVE the anchor (hint agent-relay/tui-busy-block-collapses); (2) host read end_row is INCLUSIVE 0-indexed → end = total - trailing - 1 (hint minerva-terminal/read-row-range-inclusive); (3) trailing chrome absorbs box top border + separating blanks. Live-verified per DoD: read_turn returned exactly \"Jupiter is the largest planet in our solar system.\" + status glyph — no chrome, no next draft."}
