{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eb3616292706685232a7ce81b354e","seq":4,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T22:30:45","note":"in_progress → done. Shipped plugins main 9e4da87; HITL-PASSED live 2026-06-10 post-reinstall+/mcp: one blocking call on real Claude Code returned {answer:\"The chemical symbol for gold is Au…\", cause:turn_completed, method:settle_prompt, timed_out:false} in ~10s. Composes send_core + watcher::wait_for_turn (detection_serial poll, 100ms) + read_turn_core — no duplicated logic. Timeout leaves the arm set (one-shot event still fires for triggers); default 120s clamp [1s,600s]. Depends-on items (busy-gate, row fix) landed first as planned. Integration test crosses the gated race window."}
